Clark James Gable https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Clark_James_Gable 0 Clark James Gable (born September 20, 1988 in Malibu, California), also known as Clark Gable III, is an American actor, model, and television presenter. He is the former television host of the reality show Cheaters.Gable is the grandson of the actor Clark Gable, son of John Clark Gable and Tracy Yarro, and younger brother of actress Kayley Gable. His stepfather is former Chicago bassist Jason Scheff.
